---
description: Spec-driven development workflow — specs in /specs are the source of truth
alwaysApply: true
---

Always follow specs in /specs.

Before implementing:
1. Read the related spec.
2. Create or update tests first.
3. Do not add behavior that is not described.
4. If the spec is unclear, update the spec before coding.
5. Keep features separated under `src/features/<featureName>`.
